COMPONENT CONFIGURATION
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

This component can be used in:
- Experience Cloud Communities (lightningCommunity__Default, lightningCommunity__Page)
- Lightning Record Pages (lightning__RecordPage)

Configuration Properties:
- recordId: Knowledge article version ID for direct lookup
- urlName: SEO-friendly URL name for article lookup
- language: Language override (defaults to user language)
- showTopics: Controls topic links display

